梦</a>》首演。1596年，创作的戏剧《<a","metadata":{"knowledgePointId":"693a7df3879fc42c2243fa82","loc":{"lines":{"from":1,"to":1}}}}],["20",{"pageContent":"rgb(19, 110, 194);\">仲夏夜之梦</a>》首演。1596年，创作的戏剧《<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%A8%81%E5%B0%BC%E6%96%AF%E5%95%86%E4%BA%BA/13498?fromModule=lemma_inlink\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">威尼斯商人</a>》首演。&nbsp;1601年，创作的戏剧《<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%93%88%E5%A7%86%E9%9B%B7%E7%89%B9/15196?fromModule=lemma_inlink\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">哈姆雷特</a>》首演，引起文坛关注。1603年，创作的戏剧《<a","metadata":{"knowledgePointId":"693a7df3879fc42c2243fa82","loc":{"lines":{"from":1,"to":1}}}}],["21",{"pageContent":"110, 194);\">哈姆雷特</a>》首演，引起文坛关注。1603年，创作的戏剧《<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%A5%A5%E8%B5%9B%E7%BD%97/1551?fromModule=lemma_inlink\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">奥赛罗</a>》首演。1605年，创作的戏剧《<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%9D%8E%E5%B0%94%E7%8E%8B/2286?fromModule=lemma_inlink\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">李尔王</a>》首演。1606年，创作的戏剧《<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%BA%A6%E5%85%8B%E7%99%BD/2741?fromModule=lemma_inlink\" rel=\"noopener\"","metadata":{"knowledgePointId":"693a7df3879fc42c2243fa82","loc":{"lines":{"from":1,"to":1}}}}],["22",{"pageContent":"rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">麦克白</a>》首演。1614年，离开伦敦，返回故乡<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 204);\">&nbsp;[2]</span>。1616年4月23日，威廉·莎士比亚在故乡去世<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 204);\">&nbsp;[2]</span>。</p><p>\t莎士比亚是英国文艺复兴时期伟大的诗人和戏剧家，他的作品被翻译成各国文字，在世界上广泛传播，其艺术生命力经久不衰。因此，莎士比亚成了人们道不尽的永久话题。他同时代的戏剧家本·琼森称他“既是时代的灵魂”，又“不属于一个时代，而属于所有的世纪”<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 204);\">&nbsp;[22]</span>。</p>","metadata":{"knowledgePointId":"693a7df3879fc42c2243fa82","loc":{"lines":{"from":1,"to":1}}}}],["23",{"pageContent":"Hooks are a new addition in React 16.8. They let you use state and other React features without writing a class. Common hooks include useState and useEffect.","metadata":{"knowledgePointId":"693a9b3a533023db56e89c61","loc":{"lines":{"from":1,"to":1}}}}],["24",{"pageContent":"Composition API is a set of APIs that allows us to author Vue components using imported functions instead of declaring options. It is inspired by React Hooks.","metadata":{"knowledgePointId":"693a9b3f533023db56e89c63","loc":{"lines":{"from":1,"to":1}}}}],["25",{"pageContent":"Hooks are a new addition in React 16.8. They let you use state and other React features without writing a class. Common hooks include useState and useEffect.","metadata":{"knowledgePointId":"693a9b82533023db56e89c68","loc":{"lines":{"from":1,"to":1}}}}],["26",{"pageContent":"Hooks are a new addition in React 16.8. They let you use state and other React features without writing a class. Common hooks include useState and useEffect.","metadata":{"knowledgePointId":"693a9e8d7af10bb41210da26","loc":{"lines":{"from":1,"to":1}}}}],["27",{"pageContent":"Hooks are a new addition in React 16.8. They let you use state and other React features without writing a class. Common hooks include useState and useEffect.","metadata":{"knowledgePointId":"693a9fa0e8cc01a797354b9b","loc":{"lines":{"from":1,"to":1}}}}],["28",{"pageContent":"<p>\t鲁迅（1881年9月25日—1936年10月19日），原名周樟寿，后改名周树人，字豫山，后改字豫才，<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%B5%99%E6%B1%9F/154399?fromModule=lemma_inlink\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">浙江</a><a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E7%BB%8D%E5%85%B4/15605?fromModule=lemma_inlink\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">绍兴</a>人。中国著名文学家、思想家、革命家、教育家、美术家、书法家、民主战士，<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%96%B0%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8/527309?fromModule=lemma_inlink\"","metadata":{"knowledgePointId":"693ab26a3462a43a33f7e6f8","loc":{"lines":{"from":1,"to":1}}}}],["29",{"pageContent":"rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">新文化运动</a>的重要参与者，<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E6%96%87%E5%AD%A6/8079915?fromModule=lemma_inlink\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">中国现代文学</a>的奠基人之一。鲁迅怀着现实关切，创造性地从<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%8E%E4%BC%98%E7%A7%80%E4%BC%A0%E7%BB%9F%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96/63949901?fromModule=lemma_inlink\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110,","metadata":{"knowledgePointId":"693ab26a3462a43a33f7e6f8","loc":{"lines":{"from":1,"to":1}}}}],["30",{"pageContent":"rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">中华优秀传统文化</a>中汲取营养，创作出具有中国作风、中国气派的文学作品。<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 204);\">&nbsp;[181-185]&nbsp;[187]</span>被誉为<strong>“二十世纪东亚文化地图上占最大领土的作家”。&nbsp;</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 204);\">[188]</span></p><p>\t他早年与<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%8E%89%E7%BB%A5%E4%B9%8B/18032193?fromModule=lemma_inlink\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">厉绥之</a>和<a","metadata":{"knowledgePointId":"693ab26a3462a43a33f7e6f8","loc":{"lines":{"from":1,"to":1}}}}],["31",{"pageContent":"style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">厉绥之</a>和<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%92%B1%E5%9D%87%E5%A4%AB/2586519?fromModule=lemma_inlink\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">钱均夫</a>同赴日本<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%85%AC%E8%B4%B9%E7%95%99%E5%AD%A6/3732476?fromModule=lemma_inlink\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">公费留学</a>，于日本仙台医科专门学校肄业。<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 204);\">&nbsp;[172]&nbsp;[180]</span>与<a","metadata":{"knowledgePointId":"693ab26a3462a43a33f7e6f8","loc":{"lines":{"from":1,"to":1}}}}],["32",{"pageContent":"102, 204);\">&nbsp;[172]&nbsp;[180]</span>与<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%99%88%E6%9C%9B%E9%81%93/990283?fromModule=lemma_inlink\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">陈望道</a>为保卫和发扬五四新文化运动成果、反对和冲破<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%9B%BD%E6%B0%91%E5%85%9A%E5%8F%8D%E5%8A%A8%E6%B4%BE/6800166?fromModule=lemma_inlink\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">国民党反动派</a>的文化“围剿”并肩战斗，并在斗争中建立了深厚的革命友谊<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102,","metadata":{"knowledgePointId":"693ab26a3462a43a33f7e6f8","loc":{"lines":{"from":1,"to":1}}}}],["33",{"pageContent":"style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 204);\">&nbsp;[192]</span>。</p><p>\t“鲁迅”，是他在1918年发表《<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E7%8B%82%E4%BA%BA%E6%97%A5%E8%AE%B0/11577?fromModule=lemma_inlink\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">狂人日记</a>》时所用的笔名，也是最为广泛的笔名<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 204);\">&nbsp;[1-6]</span>。鲁迅一生在<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%96%87%E5%AD%A6%E5%88%9B%E4%BD%9C/2270606?fromModule=lemma_inlink\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">文学创作</a>、<a","metadata":{"knowledgePointId":"693ab26a3462a43a33f7e6f8","loc":{"lines":{"from":1,"to":1}}}}],["34",{"pageContent":"style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">文学创作</a>、<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%96%87%E5%AD%A6%E6%89%B9%E8%AF%84/2727371?fromModule=lemma_inlink\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">文学批评</a>、思想研究、文学史研究、翻译、<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E7%BE%8E%E6%9C%AF%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA/3455200?fromModule=lemma_inlink\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">美术理论</a>引进、<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/2371144?fromModule=lemma_inlink\"","metadata":{"knowledgePointId":"693ab26a3462a43a33f7e6f8","loc":{"lines":{"from":1,"to":1}}}}],["35",{"pageContent":"rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">基础科学</a>介绍和古籍校勘与研究等多个领域具有重大贡献。他对于<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E4%BA%94%E5%9B%9B%E8%BF%90%E5%8A%A8/291670?fromModule=lemma_inlink\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">五四运动</a>以后的中国社会思想文化发展具有重大影响，蜚声世界文坛，尤其在<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%9F%A9%E5%9B%BD/6009333?fromModule=lemma_inlink\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">韩国</a>、<a","metadata":{"knowledgePointId":"693ab26a3462a43a33f7e6f8","loc":{"lines":{"from":1,"to":1}}}}],["36",{"pageContent":"style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">韩国</a>、<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC/111617?fromModule=lemma_inlink\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">日本</a>思想文化领域有极其重要的地位和影响，被誉为“二十世纪东亚文化地图上占最大领土的作家”。<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 204);\">&nbsp;[7-9]</span></p><p>\t<a href=\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%AF%9B%E6%B3%BD%E4%B8%9C/113835?fromModule=lemma_inlink\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194);\">毛泽东</a>曾评价：“鲁迅的方向，就是中华民族新文化的方向。”<span style=\"color:","metadata":{"knowledgePointId":"693ab26a3462a43a33f7e6f8","loc":{"lines":{"from":1,"to":1}}}}],["37",{"pageContent":"style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 204);\">&nbsp;[176]</span></p>","metadata":{"knowledgePointId":"693ab26a3462a43a33f7e6f8","loc":{"lines":{"from":1,"to":1}}}}],["38",{"pageContent":"<p><strong>路由守护</strong>是一种用于控制用户访问特定路由的机制，通常用于确保用户在访问某些页面之前经过验证。以下是路由守护的一些关键点：</p><p><strong style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);\">功能</strong><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);\">：路由守护可以在用户导航到特定路由之前、之后或离开某个路由时执行特定的代码逻辑，例如验证用户权限或进行数据预加载。&nbsp;</span></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);\">实现方式</strong><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);\">：在&nbsp;Vue.js&nbsp;中，可以使用全局前置守卫、单个路由守卫或组件级守卫来实现路由守护。在&nbsp;React&nbsp;中，路由守卫也可以通过类似的逻辑来控制访问。&nbsp;</span></p><p><strong style=\"color: rgba(0, 0,","metadata":{"knowledgePointId":"693adcec608f92fc2ee46885","loc":{"lines":{"from":1,"to":1}}}}],["39",{"pageContent":"style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);\">应用场景</strong><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);\">：常见的应用场景包括权限验证、登录验证和数据预加载等。&nbsp;</span></p><p>通过路由守护，可以提高应用的安全性和用户体验。</p><p><br></p>","metadata":{"knowledgePointId":"693adcec608f92fc2ee46885","loc":{"lines":{"from":1,"to":1}}}}]]